high_descs: Proceed straight to sink.
Pick up the front knife from the counter on the right of the sink.
Turn around, proceed to refrigerator.  Turn left to face refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, place knife on plate standing up on middle shelf.
Pick up the plate with knife.  Close the refrigerator.
Turn left, proceed to sink.
Put plate with knife in left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put knife on plate and move to sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the fridge, then turn left and walk over to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife off of the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn around and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the butter knife on the plate in the fridge.
Pick up the plate with the butter knife on it and close the fridge door.
Turn around and walk towards the oven, then hang a right and walk up to the sink.
Put the plate with the knife on it in the left sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a knife on it in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the sink in front of you
Pick up a butter knife to the right of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on your left.
Place the knife on a plate in the middle shelf of the fridge.
Pick up the plate from the fridge.
Turn around and walk back to the sink.
Place the plate in the left half of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a knife on it in a sink.
